{"tid":1386560,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"大家唔好諗住硬碰水炮車可以幾有效率","createTime":"2019-07-30T11:13:06.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-30T15:20:16.000Z","uid":16483,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"c0bd3b62493e7517e7668c9338e4dc9858fe3602","tid":1386560,"uid":16483,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T11:13:06.000Z","msg":"試諗下，水炮射埋黎，你根本無可能企得穩，怎至連視線都無埋。千奇唔好覺得撤退就係輸，相反要有同佢地玩既心態，啲狗每一步都要部署，每清一個區域都要準備好多野。我地唔同，只要過一兩條街又可以再玩過。切記唔好等佢射左水先走，因為到時已經會少左好多人，絕對唔係理想既方法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e92c822b6d7888d0f0a8a1c1c71a9744b6ac931b","tid":1386560,"uid":16483,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T11:15:13.000Z","msg":"要充分利用自己既優勢，唔好跟住佢地節奏。"},{"pid":"2d53ea8def2756b14ad936449d8d65851c512ab2","tid":1386560,"uid":16483,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T11:18:41.000Z","msg":"真係唔想再見到每次少幾十個，咁樣落去好快就會無晒勇武，你地既勇氣值得放係其他地方，而唔係咁易比人拉。"},{"pid":"54ceab6239444e24210403ecf365422243bbfc0d","tid":1386560,"uid":16483,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T11:30:00.000Z","msg":"又暴動<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />對抗水炮車只會比佢拉更多人。"},{"pid":"61cbf25ceaf6f3884293abbd30a13cea773652e1","tid":1386560,"uid":192630,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T15:18:24.000Z","msg":"人地出水炮...咪be water lo<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8117bbb520de00aaf14b3c823ae8cbe35a9f02cf","tid":1386560,"uid":168250,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T15:20:16.000Z","msg":"水炮車嘅出現亦都係雞尾酒來臨嘅時候"}]}